" Swap two words
nmap <silent> gw :s/\(\%#\w\+\)\(\_W\+\)\(\w\+\)/\3\2\1/<CR>`'
nmap <silent> gW :s/\(\%#[^\s]\+\)\(\_W\+\)\([^\s]\+\)/\3\2\1/<CR>`'

